                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8684" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0337</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2335 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">灯塔“引航”，新质“赋能”：中信戴卡的“数”驱“智”造转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Lighthouse Guides and New Productive Empowers: the Digital Driven and Smart Manufacturing Transformation Path of CITIC Dicastal</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘海鸥，李楠，宋婷婷，张亚明，林栋，康泰，王海英</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信戴卡股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；灯塔工厂；新质生产力；中信戴卡；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation; Lighthouse factory; New quality productivity; CITIC Dicastal</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年9月，习近平总书记强调“整合科技创新资源，引领发展战略性新兴产业和未来产业，加快形成新质生产力”。制造业是科技创新活动最活跃、科技创新成果最丰富、科技创新应用最集中的产业，如何通过新兴数字化技术实现制造企业的转型升级、培植新质生产力成为亟待解决的关键问题。案例选择全球最大的铝车轮和铝制底盘零部件供应商中信戴卡为研究对象，描述了其面临发展过程中的技术、人才、战略等瓶颈因素，如何通过数字化转型提高核心竞争力，实现企业创新与破壁发展，最终探索出了一条“数”驱“智”造转型之路，成功入选“灯塔工厂”并彰显了很强的新质生产力特征。通过分析中信戴卡进行数字化转型的动机与瓶颈，探索数字化转型的做法与经验，获悉数字化转型的价值，帮助学生理解数字化转型与瓶颈理论的相关知识点；同时，培养学生“大国智造”的责任感，鼓励学生思考如何通过中信戴卡的实践促进中国制造业转型，助力加快形成新质生产力，创新驱动制造业发展，为高质量发展注入制造业动能！</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In September 2023, General Secretary Xi Jinping emphasized the need to “integrate scientific and technological innovation resources, lead the development of strategic emerging industries and future industries, and accelerate the formation of new productive forces.” The manufacturing industry is the most active in technological innovation activities, with the richest technological innovation achievements and the most concentrated application of technological innovation. How to achieve the transformation and upgrading of manufacturing enterprises and cultivate new quality productivity through emerging digital technologies has become a key issue that urgently needs to be solved. The case study selects CITIC Dicastal, the world’s largest automobile aluminum parts manufacturing enterprise, as the research object. It describes why it has embarked on the path of digital transformation and how it has broken through technological, talent, strategic and other bottlenecks in the process of digital transformation, thereby achieving enterprise innovation and breakthrough development. Ultimately, it explores a path of “digital” and “intelligent” manufacturing transformation, and has been successfully selected as a “lighthouse factory”, demonstrating strong characteristics of new quality productivity. By analyzing the motivations and bottlenecks of CITIC Dicastal’s digital transformation, exploring the practices and experiences of digital transformation, understanding the value of digital transformation, and helping students understand the relevant knowledge points of digital transformation and bottleneck theory. At the same time, cultivate students’ sense of responsibility for “Smart Manufacturing in a Big Country”, encourage them to think about how to promote the transformation of China&#39;s manufacturing industry through the practice of CITIC Dicastal, help accelerate the formation of new quality productive forces, innovate and drive the development of the manufacturing industry, and inject manufacturing momentum into high-quality development!</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型的概念及动因；瓶颈理论及其五大核心步骤；数字化转型的发展阶段；数字化成熟度模型；生产力理论；数字化转型的价值；数字化转型的成功要素</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
